Nothing.

1227
01:08:34,311 --> 01:08:37,178
You were right
about us all along.

1228
01:08:38,581 --> 01:08:41,116
We are the devil's spawn.

1229
01:08:42,885 --> 01:08:44,619
"when someone
wants to do wrong,

1230
01:08:44,621 --> 01:08:47,589
