we can get out.

1285
01:12:01,718 --> 01:12:03,685
I love you,
christopher doll.

1286
01:12:05,487 --> 01:12:07,088
I love you, too.

1287
01:12:07,090 --> 01:12:09,490
[d]

1288
01:12:22,538 --> 01:12:25,373
[d]

1289
01:13:00,075 --> 01:13:01,142
